---
import { APP_NAME } from "@kongsian/shared/constants";
---
<section class="container" id="signup">
  <div class="card cta-card">
    <span class="eyebrow">Get started</span>
    <h2>Mulai dari satu cafe dulu.</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      Daftarkan brand kamu via WhatsApp. Onboarding &lt; 10 menit.
      Settlement pertama bisa di-generate manual untuk testing.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/6280000000000?text=Halo%20Kongsian%2C%20saya%20mau%20daftar">Chat WhatsApp</a>
      <span class="muted" style="font-size:14px">Atau email <a href="mailto:hello@kongsian.app">hello@kongsian.app</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-card { padding: 40px; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 16px; }
</style>
